sentences: Colleen Martin (born December 23, 1975), known professionally as Lady Starlight, is an American DJ and musical performer.
Starlight released her debut extended play, Untitled, in 2017.
Lady Starlight was born Colleen Martin on December 23, 1975, and was raised in upstate New York.
She moved to New York City in 2001, at the age of 26.
